OL,6,FITV News London travelled to New York
OL,7,Fto hear why the memorial is so
OL,8,Fimportant and what London may learn
OL,9,Ffor planning its own Grenfell memorial.
OL,11,FMarcio Gomes's son, Logan, was
OL,12,Fstillborn following the Grenfell fire
OL,13,Fand would like the tower to be
OL,14,Ftransformed into a high rise memorial
OL,15,Fgarden.
OL,17,F"I think the height is important,"
OL,18,FMarcio said.
