OL,6,F"The height is important because
OL,7,Fthat's where you need to be able to
OL,8,Fsee. So to take that away - that's
OL,9,Fkind of ripping my heart out," he
OL,10,Fexplained.
OL,12,FFellow Grenfell survivor Nick Burton
OL,13,Fjoined Marcio in New York and said he
OL,14,Fwas inspired by what he had seen.
OL,16,FHe said: "I didn't know there was so
OL,17,Fmuch of a struggle they went through -
OL,18,Fso many designs they had to go through.
