OL,6,F"All the planning about the materials
OL,7,Fand where it was going to be - it took
OL,8,Fthem a long, long time to to get it
OL,9,Fright. And they they got it right."
OL,11,FAnthoula Katsimatides lost her
OL,12,Fbrother, John, on 9/11. He worked on
OL,13,Fthe top floor at the World Trade
OL,14,FCentre and could not escape after the
OL,15,Fplane hit.
OL,17,F"All he did was work," Anthoula told
OL,18,FITV News London.
OL,20,F"I think about John every day - I
OL,21,Fthink about him every day.
