OL,6,F"I think the best part about our
OL,7,Fmemorial it brings us some sort of
OL,8,Fpeace just to come somewhere like this
OL,9,F- it's where he lost his soul - his
OL,10,Flife," she explained.
OL,12,FNew York's 9/11 memorial at Ground
OL,13,FZero is a tribute which honors the
OL,14,F2,977 people killed in the terror
OL,15,Fattacks of September 11, 2001 at the
OL,16,FWorld Trade Center site and also near
OL,17,FShanksville, Pennsylvania, and at the
OL,18,FPentagon.
